+FILES ON EXECUTION PATH: [moduleA.py, moduleB.py, test_multifile_bug.py]
+
+COVERAGE CHECK:
+  -- [✓] Files read ⊇ Files on execution path
+  -- [✓] Traced across at least 1 component boundary
